OMV Petrom SA (SNP)  will fire about 259
employees at its Arpechim refinery, which the company plans to
close, starting Jan. 9,  Mediafax  reported, citing Ionel Popescu,
a union leader.  Petrom will temporarily retain about 350 employees at
Arpechim to secure the refineryâ€™s shutdown, the Bucharest-based
